title: 11/11: Injuries, WR Talk, FAAB Strategies (Fantasy Football Podcasts)
description:
Dr. David Chao of ProFootballDoc.com joins us to update the listeners on Saquon Barkley, James Conner, Matthew Stafford and more. Then Will Brinson and Chris Towers hop on to look at five big Fantasy Football topics. What is the state of the WR Position through 10 weeks (14:00)? Which committee backfields are most concerning right now (26:40)? Which struggling QBs could take advantage of playoff matchups (33:00)? How should you be spending your FAAB as the playoffs approach (41:00)? And what kind of haul should you expect if you trade Lamar Jackson (44:40)?
